<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id83b39b1f-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2" identifier="/us/usc/t41/s105"><num value="105">§ 105.</num><heading> Component</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this subtitle, the term “component” means an item supplied to the Federal Government as part of an end item or of another component.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id83b39b20-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2">(<ref href="/us/pl/111/350/s3">Pub. L. 111–350, § 3</ref>, <date date="2011-01-04">Jan. 4, 2011</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/124/3680">124 Stat. 3680</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
